<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No spoilers here, please.</strong></em> <p>
Beornings are the descendants of Beorn, a powerful shapeshifter who dwells near Mirkwood. They have all inherited his shapeshifting abilities and can turn into powerful bears at will. 
</p>
<p>
